title: 'Not the Best. Flimsy Cap.'
body: Design is good. The material is ok; it's thin steel and light weight and has not got any dents so far. The cap is very flimsy. If the bottle falls, you can be sure that some part of the cap has a crack or has chipped. The seller has so far not provided any info about getting replacement caps and some generic brand which sells Speedex caps on Amazon has caps that don't fit well and leak.

title: 'Amazing Sipper'
body: I've been using this sipper bottle for a while now, and it has become an essential part of my daily routine. Its design is not only sleek but also highly functional. The sipper cap ensures that I can hydrate on the go without worrying about spills, and the flip-open lid makes it easy to clean. It's durable too, withstanding accidental drops and bumps without any issues. Whether at the gym or in the office, this sipper bottle keeps me hydrated without any fuss. Highly recommended!
